üöó App Idea ‚Äî Ultra-Clear Brief

The app connects people who live in the same building or locality and are traveling to similar destinations, so they can go together in the same car or meet up for the ride.

Problem

In big cities like Bangalore, Hyderabad, and Andhra, Many people from the same apartment/building Travel to the same areas But they go separately in different vehicles.

This causes:
Wasted fuel
Extra money spent
More traffic
No opportunity to socialize with neighbors

---

Solution (Your App)

A simple mobile app where:

1Ô∏è‚É£ Users show their live location Only within the building/locality ‚Äî not public.

2Ô∏è‚É£ They set their destination
Example: ‚ÄúGoing to Koramangala‚Äù, ‚ÄúGoing to office‚Äù, ‚ÄúGoing to city‚Äù, ‚ÄúGoing to dinner‚Äù, etc.

3Ô∏è‚É£ They set their timing
Immediate, or scheduled (ex: leaving in 20 min).

4Ô∏è‚É£ The app automatically matches people
If two or more people from the same building are going to the same destination around the same time, the app shows:

‚ÄúYou can go together‚Äù
‚ÄúYou can take the same car‚Äù
‚ÄúYou can share Uber/auto"
Or ‚ÄúYou can just go and eat together‚Äù

---

What the App Achieves

‚úî Saves money
‚úî Reduces traffic
‚úî Builds community
‚úî Very useful for apartments, hostels, working professionals
‚úî Hyper-local mobility + social app

---

MVP Features (Minimum First Version)

Only the essentials:
Signup + verify building or locality
Set availability: ‚ÄúGoing now / later‚Äù
Set destination
Real-time matching (who else is going)
Chat or contact option
Basic map / location sharing

---

Why Government Might Be Interested

Because it:
Reduces traffic
Reduces pollution
Encourages carpooling
Fits urban mobility improvement goals

So showing an MVP can help get grants or startup funding.

---

